 to go shopping for exact ingredients, so I just used what I had, and it turned out delicious! :) Thank you so much for this recipe! Here&#8217;s what I used (baked for 45 minutes at 350).</p>\n<p>cake:<br />1.5 cups all-purpose flour;<br />1 cup raw sugar;<br />1 tsp baking soda;<br />1 tsp cinnamon;<br />1 tsp ground ginger;<br />1/2 tsp nutmeg;<br />1/2 tsp salt;<br />1 med lime;<br />1 Tbsp + 1 tsp olive oil;<br />1 cup water;</p>\n<p>glaze:<br />1/2 cup brown sugar;<br />rest of the lime juice;</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2011/03/lemon-spice-cake/?replytocom=56284#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-56284\", \"56284\", \"respond\", \"13336\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"comment-58406\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/41dc3e007986c35dc46763689fa93174?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />\t\t\t\t<cite class=\"fn\">Anonymous</cite> <span class=\"says\">says:</span>\t\t \t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-meta commentmetadata\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2011/03/lemon-spice-cake/#comment-58406\">10.04.11 at 8:36 pm</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-content\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<p>Wow!  I love how you broke the cost down for this recipe.  I&#8217;m going to try it for someone who requested Lemon spice cake.  Thank you&#8230; I&#8217;m about to browse some older post.  Great Job!</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2011/03/lemon-spice-cake/?replytocom=58406#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-58406\", \"58406\", \"respond\", \"13336\")'>Reply</